title: Jon Snow's Revenge: Siege for the North - Seven Kingdoms Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
After the betrayal of Rob Stark, Jon Snow rallied a force so northern allies to bring justice to House Bolton.  The fate of the North will be decided in this Game of Thrones Siege Battle!  Enjoy!

Make sure you watch Part 1 First: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OR0Vn5ZdFak&t=3s

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
